data.description: Welcome to your new half-acre homestead in a sprawling and beautiful tree-lined subdivision.  The house features a 3-bedroom, 2 bath split floor plan which offers privacy for everyone. Enjoy entertaining in the eat-in kitchen with new appliances and center island. The generous sized living room has a wood burning fireplace, plant ledges to display your home decor, and adjoins to a dining space which can also be used as an office. The home's large windows let in natural light and views of the outdoors, front courtyard, and mature trees. The primary bedroom has a trey ceiling and an en suite bathroom with a sliding barn door, 2 walk-in closets, a jetted tub, separate shower, and a double vanity.  The bonus room, complete with built-in storage, can be used as a family room, a game room, fitness area, or hobby room. This property offers a spacious and comfortable living experience on a large lot with plenty of outdoor amenities. You can enjoy raising chickens, growing gardens, or installing a pool in the backyard, which also has a double gate and 60-amp rv hookup. The backyard overlooks a neighboring horse pasture, creating a serene and natural setting. The indoor laundry room is conveniently located right off the 2-car garage entry. The roof and water tank have been updated in 2021 and HVAC in 2019.   This property is ideal for anyone looking for some extra space for their family while still being close to shopping, great schools, town and beautiful beaches.
